01:26:03.480 --> 01:26:04.980
shows most Americans believe

01:26:05.080 --> 01:26:10.220
that neither Thomas nor his accuser
Anita Hill told the entire truth.

01:26:10.320 --> 01:26:13.100
I was hoping I could
have a quick word with you, if it's okay.

01:26:13.200 --> 01:26:15.362
