Okay, so let me start by saying

01:26:23.760 --> 01:26:26.127
I get why you've been quiet
through all of this.

01:26:27.240 --> 01:26:30.642
I'm sure a lot of people much smarter than me
have told you that's the way to go.

01:26:31.480 --> 01:26:33.369
And who knows? Maybe they're right, but...

01:26:35.080 --> 01:26:37.242
She's all alone out there, sir.

01:26:57.280 --> 01:26:58.725
You ever taken a polygraph before, Miss Hill?

01:26:59.400 --> 01:27:01.209
- No, I have not.
- Okay.

01:27:06.480 --> 01:27:07.860
WOMAN: She told me she was being subjected

01:27:07.960 --> 01:27:09.291
to sexual harassment from her boss.

01:27:10.480 --> 01:27:11.925
