01:27:12.760 --> 01:27:15.020
She told me Clarence Thomas
asked her out on dates

01:27:15.120 --> 01:27:18.140
and showed an unwanted
sexual interest in her.

01:27:18.240 --> 01:27:19.651
PATRICK: Is she, in your estimation,

01:27:19.840 --> 01:27:22.500
a woman who suffers
from fantasies in any way

01:27:22.600 --> 01:27:25.126
or is she pretty levelheaded?

01:27:25.360 --> 01:27:27.840
She's one of the most
