01:27:28.280 --> 01:27:29.260
PATRICK: Thank you, Judge.

01:27:29.360 --> 01:27:31.806
- MAN: Is your name Anita F. Hill?
- Yes.

01:27:33.920 --> 01:27:39.529
Various psychiatrists have come forward
to state as a general principle,

01:27:39.840 --> 01:27:43.128
not as a diagnosis of an individual
but as a general principle,

01:27:44.320 --> 01:27:47.927
that there is a specific disorder.

01:27:48.480 --> 01:27:52.610
So here is this foul stack of stench

01:27:53.360 --> 01:27:55.840
justifiably offensive in any category,

01:27:57.440 --> 01:28:01.081
and I ask you why, after she left his power,

01:28:01.400 --> 01:28:04.324
or whatever it was that gave her fear

01:28:04.680 --> 01:28:07.604
or revulsion or repulsion...

01:28:08.400 --> 01:28:14.123
Why did she, twice after that,
visit personally with him in Tulsa, Oklahoma?

01:28:16.800 --> 01:28:20.980
I get Christmas cards from people I don't see
from one end of the year to the other end

01:28:21.080 --> 01:28:22.286
and do not wish to.

01:28:23.160 --> 01:28:26.130
I also return their cards
and will return their calls.

01:28:27.040 --> 01:28:29.300
And these are people who have insulted me

01:28:29.400 --> 01:28:32.370
and done things which perhaps
have been degrading at times.

01:28:33.000 --> 01:28:34.923
But these are the things
you have to put up with.

01:28:35.440 --> 01:28:38.489
And being a black woman,
you have to put up with a lot.

01:28:38.920 --> 01:28:41.446
So you grit your teeth, and you do it.

01:28:46.280 --> 01:28:49.011
- Senator Kennedy.
- Thank you, Mr. Chairman.

01:28:53.280 --> 01:28:55.169
Some people just don't want to believe you.

01:28:55.600 --> 01:28:59.525
You have to understand
that they just don't want to believe you,

01:28:59.920 --> 01:29:02.321
- and they don't want to believe Professor Hill.
- (SIGHS)

01:29:04.600 --> 01:29:05.681
But I hope, Mr. Chairman...

01:29:06.600 --> 01:29:10.082
I hope that we're not going to hear
a lot more comments,

01:29:11.480 --> 01:29:14.609
unworthy, unjustified comments

01:29:14.840 --> 01:29:18.287
about fantasy stories picked out of books

01:29:18.440 --> 01:29:22.286
and law cases
after we've heard from this panel.

01:29:22.600 --> 01:29:25.809
I hope we can clear this room of the dirt

01:29:25.920 --> 01:29:30.209
and innuendo
about over-the-transom information.

01:29:32.480 --> 01:29:33.860
I hope we're going to be sensitive

01:29:33.960 --> 01:29:37.660
to the attempts of character assassination
on Professor Hill.

01:29:37.760 --> 01:29:39.046
They're unworthy.

01:29:40.280 --> 01:29:43.841
And quite frankly, I hope we're not going
to hear a lot more about racism

01:29:44.120 --> 01:29:46.122
as we consider this nominee.

01:29:46.760 --> 01:29:51.322
Fact is that these points
of sexual harassment

01:29:51.920 --> 01:29:55.811
are made by an Afro-American
against an Afro-American.

01:29:57.160 --> 01:30:00.289
The issue isn't discrimination and racism.

01:30:01.120 --> 01:30:03.805
It's about sexual harassment.

01:30:04.680 --> 01:30:10.608
And I hope we can keep our eye
on that particular issue.

01:30:13.320 --> 01:30:14.481
Thank you.

01:30:15.680 --> 01:30:17.330
JOE: Thank you, Senator Kennedy.

01:30:34.240 --> 01:30:36.100
CAROLE: Within the last few minutes,
we just found out

01:30:36.200 --> 01:30:39.620
that Professor Anita Hill
has taken a polygraph test,

01:30:39.720 --> 01:30:44.180
and according to the expert that
administered it to her, she passed it.

01:30:44.280 --> 01:30:45.940
She offered to take a lie detector test.

01:30:46.040 --> 01:30:47.900
That's not the hallmark
of someone who's lying.

01:30:48.000 --> 01:30:50.660
FEMALE REPORTER: At a golf outing,
President Bush said he saw no reason

01:30:50.760 --> 01:30:54.048
for either Hill or Judge Clarence Thomas
to take such a test.

01:30:54.440 --> 01:30:59.660
I don't want to be in a position of advocating
that every nominee takes a lie detector test.

01:30:59.760 --> 01:31:01.046
And I think it's a stupid idea.

01:31:01.600 --> 01:31:03.364
JACK: Of course she'll pass a polygraph

01:31:03.960 --> 01:31:07.851
because the disorder makes her believe
she is telling the truth.

01:31:08.080 --> 01:31:11.300
FEMALE REPORTER: Republicans complaining
bitterly that, as Orrin Hatch said,

01:31:11.400 --> 01:31:14.980
you can find any polygraph tester
to produce any results you want.

01:31:15.080 --> 01:31:19.404
He called it "the sleazy tactic
of a two-bit sleaze lawyer."

01:31:20.440 --> 01:31:22.100
MALE REPORTER:
It seems to me that in the country

01:31:22.200 --> 01:31:24.660
for that great band in the middle somewhere,

01:31:24.760 --> 01:31:28.162
that their judgment swings
from session to session.

01:31:28.480 --> 01:31:30.767
This afternoon,
Anita Hill's friends and supporters

01:31:30.880 --> 01:31:32.180
made a very credible appearance.

01:31:32.280 --> 01:31:35.100
Tonight, his friends and supporters
and coworkers

01:31:35.200 --> 01:31:36.900
are making credible performances.

01:31:37.000 --> 01:31:39.731
He's a man of high moral standing,

01:31:39.960 --> 01:31:42.088
and I tell you that it's not possible

01:31:42.480 --> 01:31:44.980
that he could be linked
with the kinds of things

01:31:45.080 --> 01:31:46.740
that have been alleged against him here.

01:31:46.840 --> 01:31:50.322
I have known Judge Clarence Thomas
for more than 30 years,

01:31:50.440 --> 01:31:56.300
and I find the allegations by Miss Hill
not only ludicrous but totally inconsistent,

01:31:56.400 --> 01:31:59.260
and in opposite to his principles
and his personality.

01:31:59.360 --> 01:32:03.843
She played the role of a meek, innocent,
shy Baptist girl from the South

01:32:04.280 --> 01:32:06.540
who was a victim of this big bad man.

01:32:06.640 --> 01:32:10.020
Chairman Thomas
that I have known for 10 years

01:32:10.120 --> 01:32:14.603
is absolutely incapable
of the abuses described by Professor Hill.

01:32:15.000 --> 01:32:16.220
In my case,

01:32:16.320 --> 01:32:20.420
she had fantasized about my being
interested in her romantically.

01:32:20.520 --> 01:32:21.806
Et tu, Brutus?

01:32:22.560 --> 01:32:24.005
You, too, Anita?

01:32:25.360 --> 01:32:27.220
FEMALE REPORTER: Extraordinary hearings
on the nomination of

01:32:27.320 --> 01:32:29.140
Judge Clarence Thomas continue

01:32:29.240 --> 01:32:32.580
and are expected
to go on long into the night.

01:32:32.680 --> 01:32:35.540
