and Judge Clarence Thomas

01:32:35.640 --> 01:32:37.940
have been invited back
to wrap up their testimony,

01:32:38.040 --> 01:32:43.100
Extraordinary is a word that may be
not quite strong enough, Carole.

01:32:43.200 --> 01:32:46.780
This thing has ground on now for hours
through the day and into the night.

01:32:46.880 --> 01:32:48.700
Some Republican senators are still trying

01:32:48.800 --> 01:32:52.060
to prevent the Committee from hearing
testimony from another witness

01:32:52.160 --> 01:32:54.060
who's come forward against Thomas.

01:32:54.160 --> 01:32:55.940
MALE REPORTER:
At first, we thought it was going to be

01:32:56.040 --> 01:32:58.300
