01:33:11.320 --> 01:33:13.641
Because he was a character witness for me?

01:33:14.480 --> 01:33:15.527
Yes.

01:33:23.000 --> 01:33:26.260
If we can get Thomas's porn rental records,
I say we get them.

01:33:26.360 --> 01:33:29.700
- Absolutely not, no.
- Joe, this is a dirty fight.

01:33:29.800 --> 01:33:31.980
There's no second place.
If we don't win, we lose.

01:33:32.080 --> 01:33:33.320
At what cost, Patrick?

01:33:33.560 --> 01:33:36.620
I'm getting calls into my office.
Hundreds an hour.

01:33:36.720 --> 01:33:37.940
American citizens saying

01:33:38.040 --> 01:33:40.060
whatever the hell
you people are doing down there

01:33:40.160 --> 01:33:45.740
with the Coke cans and Long Dong Ding,
