01:33:45.840 --> 01:33:46.940
We have an obligation to make sure

01:33:47.040 --> 01:33:48.900
we're putting the right person
on the Supreme Court.

01:33:49.000 --> 01:33:51.820
I also have an obligation
to uphold the dignity

01:33:51.920 --> 01:33:54.540
and the credibility
of the United States Senate.

01:33:54.640 --> 01:33:56.881
Yeah? How's that going?

01:34:25.080 --> 01:34:27.460
MALE REPORTER: If there is
a consensus in this nation tonight,

01:34:27.560 --> 01:34:32.441
