01:35:14.600 --> 01:35:16.020
This is a free-for-all, Joe.
There are no rules.

01:35:16.120 --> 01:35:18.860
Somebody who goes after a woman
like this with no holds barred?

01:35:18.960 --> 01:35:20.860
