01:35:20.960 --> 01:35:23.620
And if a friend of mine is attacked
in a street fight,

01:35:23.720 --> 01:35:25.722
I'm gonna pick up a crowbar.

01:35:28.480 --> 01:35:30.847
Hey, take that shit with you.

01:35:38.200 --> 01:35:39.486
