that you testify,

01:36:29.840 --> 01:36:33.060
the time constraints we find ourselves under
are making that impossible.

01:36:33.160 --> 01:36:35.481
"Time constraints"?
I've been here a day and a half.

01:36:36.360 --> 01:36:39.091
So the chairman would like
to withdraw your subpoena.

01:36:39.560 --> 01:36:42.848
He will enter your deposition
into the written record unrebutted.

01:36:43.960 --> 01:36:45.769
This agreement is by mutual consent.

01:36:46.920 --> 01:36:48.300
He would like you to sign it.

01:36:48.400 --> 01:36:49.460
What if I don't?

01:36:49.560 --> 01:36:54.441
They'll fill the time with other witnesses
so they really do run out of time.

01:37:09.040 --> 01:37:10.900
Angela Wright is not going to testify.

01:37:11.000 --> 01:37:12.604
- What?
- ALL: No!

01:37:12.720 --> 01:37:14.140
By mutual agreement, they say.

01:37:14.240 --> 01:37:15.220
WOMAN: That is bullshit.

01:37:15.320 --> 01:37:17.260
The deposition is going
into the written record,

01:37:17.360 --> 01:37:19.060
so the senators will know what she said.

01:37:19.160 --> 01:37:20.540
If they read it, which they won't.

01:37:20.640 --> 01:37:22.290
- Which they won't.
- Correct.

01:37:25.120 --> 01:37:26.929
This was a mistake.

01:37:29.400 --> 01:37:32.340
This is why I never came forward before.

01:37:32.440 --> 01:37:34.920
What good have we done?

01:37:35.480 --> 01:37:38.180
My friends' jobs are being threatened.

01:37:38.280 --> 01:37:40.180
