01:37:41.440 --> 01:37:42.420
and set the record straight.

01:37:42.520 --> 01:37:45.808
I have said everything that I came here
to say, but they don't want to hear it.

01:37:47.240 --> 01:37:50.608
They don't care. They only want to win.

01:37:51.240 --> 01:37:52.980
There's got to be something we can do.

01:37:53.080 --> 01:37:55.020
There has to be something else
that we can do.

01:37:55.120 --> 01:37:56.201
We need to get the names.

01:37:56.480 --> 01:37:58.767
(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)

01:38:02.320 --> 01:38:04.846
You all have worked very hard.

01:38:11.960 --> 01:38:17.649
