01:38:56.800 --> 01:38:58.580
JOE: Ladies, thank you so much.

01:38:58.680 --> 01:39:01.340
We certainly appreciate
your testimony here today.

01:39:01.440 --> 01:39:05.081
Obviously we didn't recognize or realize

01:39:05.200 --> 01:39:07.620
we were going to go quite as late
as we did tonight.

01:39:07.720 --> 01:39:09.051
- Senator.
- But that's...

01:39:18.160 --> 01:39:22.020
Both Professor Hill and Judge Thomas

01:39:22.120 --> 01:39:26.648
have decided not to appear tomorrow.

01:39:27.480 --> 01:39:31.405
Based on that,
this entire proceeding is ended.

01:39:36.080 --> 01:39:37.923
(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)

01:39:48.160 --> 01:39:50.740
- Fifty-two votes.
- Fifty-two votes! Congratulations!

01:39:50.840 --> 01:39:52.604
