Senate votes at 6:00 p.m. on Tuesday.

01:40:24.480 --> 01:40:27.660
But the situation is now
so muddled and so confused

01:40:27.760 --> 01:40:31.100
after three days of lurid,
inconclusive testimony

01:40:31.200 --> 01:40:33.180
that nobody's sure of anything,

01:40:33.280 --> 01:40:36.409
except that the whole process
has been distasteful.

